snippet.title: The Channel F Files VideoCart 17 Pinball Challenge Gameplay!
snippet.description: Not actually a Pinball game but Breakout :)  Still a fun game on the Fairchild Channel F System.  I used to play this game quite often while waiting for the bus to pick me up when I was a kid :)
